<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Changelog - Arsip Surat Digital Enterprise</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1a56db; --secondary: #64748b; --success: #10b981;
            --warning: #f59e0b; --danger: #ef4444; --dark: #1f2937;
            --light: #f9fafb; --lighter: #ffffff; --border: #e5e7eb;
            --font-sans: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: var(--font-sans); background: var(--light); color: var(--dark); }
        
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #7c3aed); color: white; padding: 60px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; }
        
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        .back-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        
        .version-card { background: var(--lighter); border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .version-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .version-badge { background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; }
        .version-date { color: var(--secondary); font-size: 14px; }
        .version-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
        .tag-new { background: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
        .tag-fix { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
        .tag-change { background: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
        
        .change-list { list-style: none; }
        .change-item { display: flex; gap: 10px; padding: 8px 0; font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light); }
        .change-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .change-icon { font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) { .header h1 { font-size: 24px; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>📝 Changelog</h1>
        <p style="opacity: 0.9;">Riwayat Perubahan Arsip Surat Digital Enterprise</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">← Kembali ke Beranda</a>
        
        <div class="version-card">
            <div class="version-header">
                <span class="version-badge">v2.1.0</span>
                <span class="version-date">15 Januari 2024</span>
                <span class="version-tag tag-new">Latest</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="change-list">
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> QR Code verification untuk surat</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Google Sheets cloud backup (Base64 encoded)</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Advanced search dengan multiple filters</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> System monitoring dashboard</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">🔧</span> Performance optimization pada database queries</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">🔧</span> Bug fix pada pagination surat masuk</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">🔄</span> UI/UX improvement pada dashboard</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="version-card">
            <div class="version-header">
                <span class="version-badge">v2.0.0</span>
                <span class="version-date">1 Januari 2024</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="change-list">
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Multi-instansi support</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Role-Based Access Control (5 roles)</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Progressive Web App (PWA)</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> RESTful API lengkap</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Export laporan PDF & Excel</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Docker support</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> CI/CD pipeline</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="version-card">
            <div class="version-header">
                <span class="version-badge">v1.0.0</span>
                <span class="version-date">1 Juni 2023</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="change-list">
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Initial release</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Basic CRUD surat masuk & keluar</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> Simple disposisi system</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> User authentication</li>
                <li class="change-item"><span class="change-icon">✨</span> SQLite database</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
